All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    Represents the application interface, and is the starting point of the program.
    Distance
    Utility class which contains a function used by other classes to calculate the distance between two points.
    Drone
    The class represents the attributes of a drone.
    DronePathing
    Path Finder problem while avoiding obstacles.
    FileUtilities
    Utility class that handles functionalities related to file handling, whether creating, writing, or reading a file.
    GeoJsonDeserialiser
    Utility class used to generate GeoJson strings which contain methods to make Features of sensor locations and the final flight path of the drone.
    JsonParser
    Utility class that handles parsing data from the webserver from Json into appropriate Object types
    NoFlyZone
    Represents the confinement area and the offLimit areas on the map.
    PathNode
    Node corresponding to the properties of a point in our path search space for A* Search algorithm in DronePathing.
    RoutePlanner
    The class tackles the Traveling Salesmen Problem using TwoOpt for finding the estimated, best journey given a list of sensor points and a starting point, which we need to visit once.
    Sensor
    Class used when parsing JSON sensor information from webserver.
    What3WordsDetails
    Template class for the what3words details which will be retrieved from the webserver and converted from JSON format to this type.
    What3WordsDetails.Coordinates  
    What3WordsDetails.W3WSquare  
    What3WordsDetails.W3WSquare.SouthWestPoint
